subject: Help the Writing Center Help You
content: Dear Lianghui Yi,Thank you for visiting the Georgetown University Writing Center. We would like to know more about how your session went. Please fill out our anonymous feedback form.To complete the form, please visit the following website: https://georgetown.mywconline.com/survey.php?machid=sc64dd0647ad06fThank you!----------------To opt out, log in to https://georgetown.mywconline.com and then select 'Profile & Communication Options' from the welcome menu.
